content: I'm excited to try roasting kale and butternut squash together. I've been trying to reduce food waste by using up all the produce I buy, and I think this recipe will help me use up some of the kale I have in my fridge. Speaking of reducing food waste, I've also been saving money by buying in bulk and freezing items like beans, rice, and pasta. My pantry is finally organized and I can see everything I have, no more expired cans hidden in the back.
